11
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,520
Hey. Where would you like to have fun?

12
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,680
Eat or go to the seaside?

13
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,040
Eat, of course.

14
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,000
Tonghao.

15
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,400
Come here.

16
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,800
What’s up?

17
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:57,920
It comes to me that

18
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,600
you look like someone.

19
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,400
Who?

20
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:03,840
This guy looks like you. Right?

21
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,360
Yes, kind of.

22
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,880
Who is it?

23
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,120
It’s billionaire Shan Junhao,

24
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:19,960
the former general manager of Senwell.

25
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,055
He is said

26
00:02:21,055 --> 00:02:22,520
to be a commercial genius.

27
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,920
He became the general manager at a young age.

28
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,320
Besides,

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,600
he was mysterious and low-profile.

30
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:30,360
He seldom attends

31
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,640
the interviews from any media.

32
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,200
This photo

33
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,520
was taken by a gossip reporter

34
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,400
with great difficulty.

35
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,840
Show me today’s

36
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,360
housing registration form.

37
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,000
OK.

38
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,240
Senwell?

39
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,880
Isn’t Senwell’s general manager Zhang Minghan?

40
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,240
Shan Junhao was the former one.

41
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:57,760
It’s said he went abroad to further his studies.

42
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,200
That’s why Zhang Minghan replaced his position.

43
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:04,120
He’s so handsome in this photo.

44
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,360
Although his face isn’t clear,

45
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,000
I can still

46
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,760
feel his noble temperament all over

47
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,520
through the screen.

48
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,720
Can you feel it?

49
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,400
So charming.

50
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,360
Tonghao.

51
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,120
Come out with me.

52
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,000
I have a business for you.

53
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,200
What is it?

54
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,760
Do me a favor

55
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,440
to offset half of the money you owe me.

56
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,040
It’s a good deal, isn’t it?

57
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,560
What’s the favor?

58
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,240
Go to my classmate party with me.

59
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:42,120
Taichu can’t go,

60
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,320
so you want me be his substitute?

61
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,000
Only you can help me.

62
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,680
I am not a rich man.

63
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,320
What’s my identity for the party?

64
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,760
My boyfriend.

65
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,960
Your boyfriend?

66
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:04,320
Why not let someone else be your boyfriend?

67
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,000
There are few men in Guanmei Fishing Village.

68
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,480
You want Sheng to play my boyfriend?

69
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:11,480
Sheng likes Su Liyin.

70
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,960
I can’t do that.

71
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:19,520
You are born with extraordinary temperament.

72
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,520
Handsome and sunny.

73
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:21,520
Who else can be my boyfriend

74
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,600
if not you?

75
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,880
If you say so,

76
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,520
I may consider it.

77
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,720
Really?

78
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,840
You are close to Taichu.

79
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,880
It’s convenient to disguise as him.

80
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,200
Disguise as Taichu?

81
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,120
What do you mean?

82
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:44,000
I told Dai Anfen

83
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,680
I have a rich boyfriend.

84
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:46,880
So...

85
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,560
So you need to disguise as Taichu.

86
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,720
Qianyu.

87
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,680
You are so vainglorious.

88
00:04:57,725 --> 00:04:59,320
I am not.

89
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:01,760
Dai Anfen and Mike try to make a fool of me.

90
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,960
I won’t let that happen.

91
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,600
If you don’t like them,

92
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,840
just stay away from them.

93
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,800
Why did you brag and show off to them?

94
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,120
You made the trouble.

95
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,520
Handle it by yourself.

96
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,440
I am kind to you.

97
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,000
You must help me.

98
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,440
And

99
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,320
I have promised you

100
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,840
to reduce half of your debt.

101
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,880
If you still think it’s unfair,

102
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,920
how about two thirds?

103
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:29,880
Ye Qianyu.

104
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,600
Not all things

105
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,120
can be measured by money.

106
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,400
I don’t know

107
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,880
you are so vain

108
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,640
until now.

109
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,600
You don’t help me.

110
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,880
Why do you scold me?

111
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,600
Is it vain of me to pretend to be rich?

112
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,200
Do I deserve to be mocked

113
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,280
and despised?

114
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,800
Why not be your true self in front of them?

115
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,280
I’m not rich.

116
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,480
Go to ask someone else for help.

117
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,920
You do look like him.

118
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,760
Why not disguise as him

119
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,560
and go to the party with my sister?

120
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,320
Why do you let me pretend to be the rich?

121
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,680
Is it shameful to be poor?

122
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,640
Why can’t I

123
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,960
go to the party with my true identity?

124
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,280
Move to that side.

125
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,440
Let me tell you.

126
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,600
My sister loved a boy

127
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,840
named Mike in school.

128
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,520
Her classmate Dai Anfen made a fool of her

129
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,800
and said Mike liked her too.

130
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,480
She even

131
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:46,680
asked her to confess her love to Mike at a party.

132
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:50,000
Mike deliberately asked her to dance in public,

133
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:51,960
but rejected her.

134
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,200
From then on,

135
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,120
her classmates nicknamed her Clumsy Dance Queen.

136
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,720
Your sister loves so many boys.

137
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,320
Oh, right.

138
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,720
Wait a second. Let me show you something.

139
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,480
Is your car repaired?

140
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,360
My old pickup often breaks down.

141
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,840
I have to repair it every three or five days.

142
00:07:28,125 --> 00:07:28,902
Thanks to it,

143
00:07:28,902 --> 00:07:30,520
I’m adept at repairing cars now.

144
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,360
Mama Jinzhi said

145
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,600
you would have a classmate party tomorrow. Right?

146
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,800
Yes.

147
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,840
Is this party special?

148
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,280
You know

149
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,600
classmate parties.

150
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,560
They wear the best clothes,

151
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,120
take the best bags

152
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,400
and drive the best cars

153
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,960
to show off themselves.

154
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:00,280
But I have nothing to show off.

155
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,200
I made a trouble for myself.

156
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,240
I’m sure

157
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,920
they will make fun of me tomorrow.

158
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,480
What trouble?

159
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,960
Ye Qianyu keeps a diary.

160
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:17,320
She writes down everything, including secrets,

161
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,160
in the diary.

162
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,640
Wait a second.

163
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,920
My mom couldn’t afford storybooks for me,

164
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,360
so I read her diary.

165
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,120
It’s much more interesting

166
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,160
than the storybooks.

167
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,440
Let me see.

168
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:34,680
This diary

169
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,920
is about Dai Anfen and Mike making a fool of her.

170
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:37,800
Look.

171
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:39,600
These words were blurred

172
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,800
by her tears.

173
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,800
Please have pity on her.

174
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,800
I had a crush on my classmate before.

175
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,800
He made fun of me

176
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,720
and asked me to dance in public.

177
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:57,440
Yesterday

178
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,960
I ran into him at Guanmei.

179
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,120
To anger him,

180
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,200
I said

181
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,960
I have a rich boyfriend.

182
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,800
I didn’t expect

183
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,640
he invited me to a classmate party

184
00:09:06,875 --> 00:09:08,400
with a boyfriend.

185
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:10,320
If he won’t see my boyfriend,

186
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,440
he will spread my awkward dance videos

187
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,840
all over the world.

188
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,920
I do want to watch your awkward dance videos.

189
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:27,880
I never want to watch it.

190
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,400
Girls tend to hide their feelings.

191
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:33,160
Although my sister wants to marry a rich man,

192
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:36,160
and my mom also wants her to marry Taichu,

193
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,400
I think

194
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,680
you still have a great chance.

195
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,320
You must seize it.

196
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:43,640
Taichu can’t go.

197
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,800
You may disguise as a rich man

198
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,280
and go to the party with my sister.

199
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:51,240
It’s a rare opportunity to get close to her.

200
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,560
I am not rich.

201
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,960
I don’t want to disguise as him.

202
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,560
But

203
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,600
Tonghao is right.

204
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:05,800
It isn’t a shame to be poor

205
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,240
or have no boyfriend.

206
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,880
I shouldn’t be afraid of Dai Anfen.

207
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,520
I should stand in front of her

208
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,560
and tell her

209
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,440
who I am.

210
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,800
That’s the right way to fight back.

211
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:25,760
Yes.

212
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,160
I am who I am.

213
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,600
I am who I am.

214
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,000
I am who I am.

215
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,520
The party will be held tomorrow.

216
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,680
You must go to save my sister.

217
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,560
Or else she will be extremely embarrassed.

218
00:10:40,950 --> 00:10:43,360
She always hopes a Prince Charming

219
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:46,440
can show up and rescue her when she’s in distress.

220
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,680
This is your chance.

221
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,000
You must seize it.

222
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,400
Tonghao.

223
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,240
Just disguise as Taichu

224
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,960
and go to the party with Qianyu.

225
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:49,640
Just go.

226
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,000
It’s not a big deal.

227
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,200
Right?

228
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,440
I’m going to deliver the goods.

229
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,520
If you don’t go,

230
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,000
Dai Anfen will embarrass Qianyu.

231
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,400
Alas. Tonghao.

232
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,800
I’m leaving.

233
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,320
Mom.

234
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,520
You take care of the store.

235
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,200
I will get prepared

236
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,880
to go to the party.

237
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,600
Neither Tonghao nor Taichu will go with you.

238
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,640
How will you go?

239
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,760
I’ve made up my mind.

240
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,275
I will tell Dai Anfen

241
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,440
I don’t have a rich boyfriend.

242
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:32,000
I lied to her.

243
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,000
She made a fool of you.

244
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,640
Now you will go ask for an insult.

245
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:37,240
Don’t go.

246
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:37,800
No.

247
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,800
I will.

248
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,240
I will tell her loudly

249
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,200
who I am.

250
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:50,880
What’s this?

251
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,480
It was from Taichu.

252
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,480
He also specially

253
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,800
sent the car key to you.

254
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,160
Taichu?

255
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:32,800
Ye Qianyu doesn’t seem to come today.

256
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:33,600
Right.

257
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,240
We can’t watch the show prepared for her.

258
00:13:36,725 --> 00:13:38,776
I knew she would not come.

259
00:13:39,025 --> 00:13:40,100
Funny.

260
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,200
It doesn’t matter.

261
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,480
Ye Qianyu.

262
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,400
Where’s your boyfriend?

263
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,280
Dai Anfen.

264
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:06,400
I come to tell you...

265
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:07,880
Attention, please.

266
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:11,520
Look who comes here.

267
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,960
It is our Clumsy Dance Queen.

268
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:16,280
Let’s welcome her.

269
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:22,960
Qianyu.

270
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:26,240
Where is your boyfriend?

271
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:28,360
You said he would come with you.

272
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,720
Why do you come alone?

273
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:35,720
Did you lie to me?

274
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:38,760
I...

275
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,240
Mike.

276
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:42,280
Ziqian?

277
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,425
I thought you wouldn’t come.

278
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,520
This is my girlfriend Dai Anfen.

279
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,360
This is Xu Ziqian,

280
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,880
the friend I mentioned to you before.

281
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:51,240
Hello.

282
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,120
Hello.

283
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,400
This is my friend Fan Yunyi.

284
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:55,200
Hello.

285
00:15:55,400 --> 00:15:56,025
Hello.

286
00:15:56,725 --> 00:15:58,120
You come so late.

287
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,680
The traffic was heavy. Sorry.

288
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,600
Never mind.

