508
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:56,360
Ye Qianyu. You’re so lucky.

509
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,880
Yes, indeed.

510
00:30:10,840 --> 00:30:12,160
Are you unhappy

511
00:30:12,360 --> 00:30:13,440
