575
00:35:18,600 --> 00:35:20,240
I’m so happy today.

576
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:22,840
I used to dream

577
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,680
Prince Charming could come

578
00:35:25,680 --> 00:35:26,880
